NagVis Template Darkglass PNP 0.4 Quick Installation Instructions
------------------------------------------

Author: Michael Luebben
Document Version: 0.4
Date: 2008-02-27
------------------------------------------

STEP 0: Prepair System
------
Make sure your System meets the requirements:
- Nagios is running
- Working NagVis 1.3x installation

STEP 1: Download Template
------
Get NagVis-Templates, the latest test release can be found at www.nagvis.org

STEP 2: Unpack Template
------
Unpack NagVis Template in a path of your choice

> tar xvzf NagVis-Template-<name>-.x.tar.gz

STEP 3: Install NagVis-Template
------
Place the NagVis-Template directory tree into your NagVis Folder (default /usr/local/nagios/share).

> cp -r nagvis /usr/local/nagios/share/nagvis/.

STEP 4: Configure
------
Open with the WUI "NagVis configuration", select for hover- and headertemplate "darkglass" and save the configuration. 
Ready! Now can use NagVis with the new Template-Design. 

Have fun and please report bugs!
